                                                                    src="../images/logo/location.png" alt="phone"
                                                                    class="lazy"></span>
                                                            <div class="content-info-support"><a href="tel:0986744591"
                                                                    class="txt-info-sp">0986.744.591</a></div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="item-info-box-support"><span class="icon"><img
                                                                    src="../images/logo/location.png" alt="email"
                                                                    class="lazy"></span>
                                                            <div class="content-info-support"><a
                                                                    href="mailto:cskh@laptopDong.com.vn"
                                                                    class="txt-info-sp mail-sp">cskh@laptopDong.com.vn</a>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="item-info-box-support"><span class="icon"><img
                                                                    src="../images/logo/location.png" alt="address"
                                                                    class="lazy"></span>
                                                            <div class="content-info-support">
                                                                <p class="txt-info-sp">186 Võ Thị Sáu,
                                                                    Quận 10, TP. HCM</p>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
